window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Spicy NA paranormal romance for fans of Jennifer L. Armentrout, Sarah J. Maas, and Laura Thalassa.<br> <br> He’s tortured. She’s broken. Together, they must take down the most legendary beast of all.</p> <p>Ferris was nothing but a heartbroken human before he met a sweet vampire who saved him from death. So when she was locked away by the vicious Queen of Hearts, he had no problem leaving his grief-stricken past behind to become immortal and rescue her. Now, Ferris will need to save her from something new—herself.</p> <p>Mouse left her mortal life behind centuries ago after a heinous event nearly destroyed her. She would never have guessed that her new life would eventually steal her happiness too. Feeling trapped by her own mind, she sets off to battle her inner demons, despite her sudden unquenchable thirst for blood. When the most terrifying beast in Wonderland emerges from the shadows, it wants destruction. Mouse won’t let her friends sacrifice themselves and makes it her mission to destroy the creature with Ferris at her side. Only this time, there’s more than friendship brewing between Mouse and Ferris, igniting a sexual tension that has been waiting to surface for years. If they don’t destroy the beast, their bond and world will crumble. </p> <p>Knave is the third book in the Vampires of Wonderland series with sizzling romance, friends to lovers, and sexy vampires.</p>"; 
